text: Müzeyyen Senar (July 16, 1918 – February 8, 2015) was a Turkish classical music performer. She was known as the "Diva of the Turkish Republic". Senar died in İzmir, Turkey from pneumonia, aged 96. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1918 births Category:2015 deaths Category:Deaths from pneumonia Category:Infectious disease deaths in Turkey Category:Turkish singers
